Online Blind Deconvolution (OBD) Demo
Version 0.0, 10-Sep-2009


This demo requires Matlab. It was tested with Matlab version R2008a.
To launch the demo just start a Matlab session, type

>> demo

and press enter. 

The following files are included in this demo version

demo.m            Intro to OBD
demo.fig          Matlab's corresponding fig file
obd_demo.m        OBD demo
obd_demo.fig      Matlab's corresponding fig file
obd.m             Implementation of OBD
obd_script.m      Script file  for demo example 

For any comments, suggestions or questions feel free 
to send an email to michael.hirsch@tuebingen.mpg.de


